								<layout columns="1 " ruledLines="22 36" writtenLines="22 36">
									<p>Uniform layout. </p>
									<p>Regular layout with ruling by black plummet. Last written line outside ruling. </p>
									<p>Titles and initial words given in large characters. </p>
									<p>Catchwords on every verso, in smaller letters, often highlighted with pen and ink. </p>
									<p>Occasional infralinear vocalization. </p>
